  <summary date="2016-02-09T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in House">Community Bank Reporting Relief Act

 This bill amends the Federal Deposit Insurance Act to direct federal banking agencies to issue regulations that allow a reduced reporting requirement for highly rated and well-capitalized depository institutions meeting certain other criteria when making the first and third report of condition for a year.</summary>
